{"tid":1557812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成班撚樣 睇陳奕迅重要啲 定 公義重要呀?","createTime":"2019-09-10T09:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:45:30.000Z","uid":66171,"like":25,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b472f1a2a00900d7e9d8228fab0e6d4418d327a8","tid":1557812,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"成班人係度求飛求飛 <br />\n一班人就食黃牛都唔緊要 另一班人就係咁放黃牛<br />\n<br />\n根本你地過去幾個星期出嚟 或者 本身你係黃底嘅原因都只係因為<br />\n羊群心理 同埋 你地係比既得利益者打壓<br />\n根本唔係真心追求公義 公平<br />\n<br />\n口口聲聲話自己追求公義 然後就自己做埋啲唔公義嘅野 助長黃牛黨 為咗小小利益就可以 犧牲公義公平<br />\n<br />\n你地有撚資格屌林奠呀? 根本你地就同一類人 只係你咁啱唔係既得利益者 佢係 然後你就拎哂光環話為咗公平公義 收撚皮啦 好撚噁心<br />\n<br />\n屌我分化撚都係咁話 入去個熱門po睇下自己個樣有幾衰啦 黃牛閪<br />\n<br />\n利申: 無諗住睇 唔洗屌我係無飛先9up"},{"pid":"8c4d95d672dcc177b0eb4a2a830b689dbe2d27d4","tid":1557812,"uid":66171,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"喂 買樓好貴呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n<br />\n你地自己攞嚟架 只係唔同市場咋 如果你有能力 你都會係嗰啲人 所以你無撚資格屌樓貴呀<br />\n<br />\n黃牛閪"},{"pid":"91a3c4e02f66802820d35e4ac032cd938ccc4018","tid":1557812,"uid":277144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"仲聽呢D偽人？<br />\n收撚皮啦"},{"pid":"8fe8a637a93cc16a134077c76a6a2fbb53217f38","tid":1557812,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b9df5fa9904bd9b6ea3866c8dfc1b4d11eeaf2","tid":1557812,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"原價收480 680 任何日子2連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0740d